<http://ns.inria.fr/pgxo/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "- Move namespace from http://pgxo.loria.fr/ to http://ns.inria.fr/pgxo/\n- Remove usage of DUL\n- Add a new data property to connect pharmacogenomic relationships to their level of evidence in ClinPGx"@en .
<http://ns.inria.fr/pgxo/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "PGxO aims at providing a small set of concepts and roles that may type elements of pharmacogenomic relationships."@en .
<http://ns.inria.fr/pgxo/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "PGxO: a lite Pharmacogenomic Ontology"@en .
<http://ns.inria.fr/pgxo/> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionInfo> "0.6" .
